位于成都市中心城区的武侯区，区内河流密集，共有大小河道45条、总长158公里。改革开放初期粗放式发展模式，一度让武侯饱受水污染困扰；近年来，成都市武侯区在推进河长制改革过程中，多措并举，实现了河长制从“有名”到“有实”的转变，水环境质量持续改善，水生态品质不断提高，沿河“脏乱带”蝶变生态“产业带”，城市水生态价值不断彰显——如今，水于武侯而言，既是“绿水”亦是“金山”。","type":"cnt_article"}],"copyright_status":"0","del_flag":"0","desc":"成都，是一座因水而兴、因水而荣的历史文化名城。位于成都市中心城区的武侯区，区内河流密集，共有大小河道45条、总长158公里。改革开放初期粗放式发展模式，一度让武侯饱受水污染困扰；近年来，成都市武侯区……","ext":{"action":{"FallSizePic":"1","Fimgurl10":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_960495/0","Fimgurl11":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_300240/0","Fimgurl18":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364726_640330/0","Fimgurl24":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_1164606/0","Fimgurl26":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_640470/0","Fimgurl28":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_1200490/0","Fimgurl29":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_580328/0","Fimgurl30":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_870492/0","Fimgurl31":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_196130/0","Fimgurl32":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_294195/0","Fimgurl4":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_450330/0","Fimgurl5":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_640330/0","Fimgurl7":"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_ls/0/12065364708_150120/0","FisUserPickEnabled":"1","OMGCategory":-2,"browser_tag":{"tag":{"0":{"id":"1041525","is_valid_tag":false,"name":"武侯区","score":1,"type":"tag"},"1":{"id":"108865946","is_valid_tag":false,"name":"河长制工作","score":0.68505555,"type":"tag"},"2":{"id":"105164964","is_valid_tag":false,"name":"河长制","score":0.60586274,"type":"tag"},"3":{"id":"1000363","is_valid_tag":false,"name":"成都","score":0.60041857,"type":"tag"},"4":{"id":"1461706","is_valid_tag":false,"name":"改革","score":0.54814744,"type":"tag"},"5":{"id":"99884951","is_valid_tag":true,"name":"江安河","score":0.5209483,"type":"tag"},"6":{"id":"108860009","is_valid_tag":false,"name":"巡河","score":0.5,"type":"tag"},"7":{"id":"1005756","i